strings: <voice_0x010011F1><se_low>Dominico: I didn't know you from Adam, but still I took you in. And THIS is how you repay me!?

<voice_0x010011F2><se_def>David: I, I didn't do anything!
Please believe me!
I, I was just feeding Leopold as norm<endash>
<voice_0x010011F3><se_low>Dominico: WHAT!? What did you call him?

<voice_0x010011F4><se_low>Dominico: It's Sir Leopold!
Just who do you think you are!?

<voice_0x010011F6><se_low>Dominico: Has this imbecile upset you too, Sir Leopold?
Of course he has!
<voice_0x010011F7><se_low>Dominico: Such impertinence! And as if omitting your title wasn't enough, no doubt the vile layabout's late feeding you too, hm?

<voice_0x010011F8><se_def>David: P-Please, Master! D-Don't be angry!
I'm more than happy to serve Leopold<endash> Ah, ah, Sir Leopold his dinner whenever he wants it.
<voice_0x010011F9><se_low>Dominico: And well you should be! ...Get on with it then, you disgusting little maggot.

<voice_0x010011FB><se_low>Dominico: Well, Sir Leopold, enjoy your dinner <endash>
now that it's FINALLY arrived. Hmph.
<voice_0x010011FC><se_low>Dominico: David! Sir Leopold is as much your master as I am! I shouldn't have to remind you that you treat him with the utmost respect! Understood!?
<voice_0x010011FD><se_low>Dominico: Ah, you're back! Ha ha! I, er, I apologise for my servant's unsightly display.
<voice_0x010011FE><se_low>Dominico: So what are you doing here? If you've come to report back, I'll, er, be waiting in my room.
